item.title: Best Dad Ever T-Shirt - White Ukelele Chords Design for Fathers
item.description: This design is for fathers who love playing the uke. Give it as a gift on a shirt, mug or other product for birthday, Christmas, Father’s Day or any other day you want to show your father that you love him. / The design reads BEST DAD EVER with DAD written using ukulele chord diagrams. Keep on strumming this lovely instrument and being a great father. • Also buy this artwork on apparel, phone cases, home decor, and more.
